lication/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-1526156078525294v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by jeetinsight", "description": "Lanthimos refused to explain the ending, saying mystery was essential.\n\nDogtooth (2009), directed by Yorgos Lanthimos, is one of the most unsettling and unique films of modern European cinema. The story explores extreme family control, isolation, and the ways people can manipulate reality.\n\nThe film’s intense scenes were filmed with practical effects, minimal music, and precise acting choices to maintain tension and unease. Actors were instructed to keep emotional reactions minimal, adding to the eerie, controlled atmosphere. Critics call it one of the most controversial and talked-about films in recent years, praised for its bold storytelling, strange world-building, and unforgettable visual style. \n.\n.\n.\n#dogtooth #yorgoslanthimos #lanthimos #psychologicalthriller #darkcinema #cinephile #movielovers #cinemalover #europeancinema #jeetinsight", "duration": 7.3, "timestamp": 1761489634, "uploader_id": "69484329435", "uploader": "Jeet Insight", "channel": "jeetinsight", "like_count": 14394, "comment_count": 74, "comments": [{"author": "adamgregory01", "author_id": "68317621370", "id": "18083607065463232", "text": "🔥🔥🔥", "timestamp": 1772732803}, {"author": "madisteinmetz17", "author_id": "79951756635", "id": "18129068203534896", "text": "Name?", "timestamp": 1771632626}, {"author": "rollingkaro", "author_id": "1582724440", "id": "18040710923749984", "text": "and yet I watched it at 16 year old age maybe this is what’s wrong with me", "timestamp": 1771032953}, {"author": "zarkrajputofficial", "author_id": "47623169306", "id": "18096945061738580", "text": "🔥🙌❤️❤️❤️", "timestamp": 1770305028}, {"author": "avastafford", "author_id": "1453650751", "id": "18327747052168694", "text": "So good", "ti